title: Hermitcraft 8 Episode 19: Building Grian's SPOOKY ALLEY!
author: GoodTimesWithScar
description:
Limited Time Swaggon Merch link: https://represent.com/store/goodtimeswithscar

Hermitcraft season 8 episode 19! We start out Ep 19 of Hermitcraft S8 by finding the Moon is still getting bigger and with earthquakes now. I investigate to see if Bdubs is behind the moon and start Grian's spooky back-alley in his midnight alley megabase. I hope you like the new build and see you in the next episode!


Hermitcraft Season 8 playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSCZsQa9VSCdDJmIMkIuK0XazfnI677oV
